be a mere fairy from Jixing Abyss.

272
00:27:31,400 --> 00:27:32,360
Yes.

273
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:34,960
Judging from Ming Yi's expression

274
00:27:35,040 --> 00:27:37,240
