320
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:42,880
Let me handle it.

321
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,120
This…

322
00:30:58,880 --> 00:30:59,840
Alright.

323
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:04,800
How is he?

324
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:12,080
To die in a beauty's arms is romantic.

325
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:16,480
I can't watch this.

326
00:31:28,920 --> 00:31:31,800
-I'm fine.
-You're still injured.

327
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:36,680
Didn't you see enough already?

328
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:50,280
Master.

329
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:52,920
I was wounded by Zhulong too.
Why am I fine?

330
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:55,880
And why did she only let me
enter the Bo clan's ancestral home?

331
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:59,200
Zhulong has a really strange temper.

332
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:02,000
Maybe she just likes you and hates him.

333
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:06,600
-Then… Then Fairy Bo…
-Enough.

334
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:07,840
What matters most right now

335
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:10,280
is finding Diwu tree's core
to make Golden Millet Dream.

336
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:18,400
Take me back to Wugui Sea
to heal my wound.

337
00:32:25,080 --> 00:32:26,240
Why are you looking at me like that?

338
00:32:26,320 --> 00:32:28,080
You can send him there.
Leave me out of this.

339
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:34,400
Where does it hurt again?

340
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:12,960
Slow down.

341
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:17,320
I'll go get Blood-Calming Powder.

342
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:19,480
Ming Yi!

343
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:28,480
You're injured.

344
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,240
Has Ming Yi come too?

345
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:32,640
-Where is she?
-Buxiu.

346
00:33:36,040 --> 00:33:36,880
I…

347
00:33:42,960 --> 00:33:43,880
No need to close the door.

348
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:45,280
Ming Yi will be back soon.

349
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:27,360
What are you doing?

350
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,199
Checking my wound.

351
00:34:46,600 --> 00:34:48,040
Are you trying to murder your husband?

352
00:34:51,239 --> 00:34:53,639
Immortal Ji, mind your words.

353
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:55,840
Our relationship is fake from the start.

354
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:58,040
Let alone now.

355
00:34:58,120 --> 00:35:00,280
Go to Marriage Stone and take a look then.

356
00:35:00,360 --> 00:35:01,840
See if our names are still there.

357
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:04,720
But those are fake names.

358
00:35:05,920 --> 00:35:07,520
Yes.

359
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:08,640
But

360
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:12,120
I carved them there at a real cost.

361
00:35:20,440 --> 00:35:24,080
I once thought you
were a descendant of the Bo clan.

362
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:29,160
I have my own family too.

363
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:32,800
My mother once left a mark
between my brows,

364
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:38,040
but I no longer wish to look for them.

365
00:35:40,520 --> 00:35:43,560
Do you fear they abandoned you?

366
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:53,880
But if Fairy Bo's your master,

367
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:56,160
