let you through?

368
00:35:58,960 --> 00:36:00,880
Perhaps it's her divine consciousness
that decided so.

369
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:03,280
Maybe she just doesn't wish to see me.

370
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:07,400
Master must be hiding something from me.

371
00:36:08,600 --> 00:36:10,360
I still don't understand that line.

372
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:12,520
"The truth lies before my eyes."

373
00:36:13,160 --> 00:36:14,400
What does it really mean?

374
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,800
Did she leave anything for you?

375
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:21,320
Only Golden Millet Dream.

376
00:36:21,400 --> 00:36:24,040
But Golden Millet Dream
cannot hold divine consciousness.

377
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:31,600
You can so naturally mention
Golden Millet Dream in front of me now.

378
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,920
You stopped pretending too.

379
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,840
You clearly know everything
about Wugui Sea,

380
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,760
even where the Blood-Calming Powder is.

381
00:36:55,920 --> 00:36:58,400
What do you plan to do next?

382
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:10,560
Now that I know the recipe
for Golden Millet Dream,

383
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,720
even if everyone says

384
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:14,920
Diwu tree's core has vanished
from Six Realms,

385
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:19,080
I still won't sit here and wait to die.
I'll go find it.

386
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:20,880
I destroyed

387
00:37:22,080 --> 00:37:23,800
Golden Millet Dream right
before your eyes.

388
00:37:25,080 --> 00:37:26,080
Don't you hate me for that?

389
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:29,360
It was yours to begin with.

390
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:32,360
You can do whatever you want with it.

391
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:36,680
