handled it properly.

393
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:43,880
You…

394
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:45,840
You suffered, didn't you?

395
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:49,720
You couldn't even enter the ancestral home

396
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:51,880
