397
00:37:51,960 --> 00:37:52,960
Fairy Bo's words…

398
00:37:53,040 --> 00:37:55,040
Master's wronging me is nonsense.

399
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:58,480
She chose to give you the recipe

400
00:37:58,560 --> 00:37:59,840
for her own reasons.

401
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:03,600
As for what she hid from me,

402
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:05,480
I'll find out myself.

403
00:38:18,520 --> 00:38:20,160
-What's wrong? Does the wound hurt again?
-What…

404
00:38:25,600 --> 00:38:26,840
I'm hungry.

405
00:38:29,920 --> 00:38:31,160
Come eat with me.

406
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:38,760
Ji Bozai, are you
incapable of taking care of yourself?

407
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:40,840
You need company even to eat?

408
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:43,360
I got hurt because of you.

409
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:47,120
Slow down.
At least change into clean clothes.

410
00:38:47,200 --> 00:38:48,640
Fine.

411
00:38:51,800 --> 00:38:53,160
You said you were hungry.

412
00:38:53,240 --> 00:38:54,680
I brought the food inside,
yet you wouldn't eat.

413
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,640
You had to come here to eat.
What are you doing?

414
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:01,440
Why are you covering my eyes? Ji Bozai.

415
00:39:03,560 --> 00:39:04,840
Put your hand down.

416
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,080
You're not in pain anymore, are you?

417
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:10,720
Why are you covering my eyes?
Eat by yourself then.

418
00:39:30,520 --> 00:39:31,480
Embers.

419
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:36,520
I return Embers to you today.

420
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:39,560
From now on,
whether you stay in Jixing Abyss

421
00:39:40,120 --> 00:39:41,640
or return to Yaoguang Mountain,

422
00:39:42,640 --> 00:39:44,360
it will always protect you.

423
00:39:49,800 --> 00:39:52,080
I can only try to restore its appearance,

424
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:55,680
but only you can truly repair it
completely.

425
00:39:56,800 --> 00:39:57,920
Thank you.

