I dare not hope for a future.

438
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:08,080
Do you want to eat fish?

439
00:41:08,160 --> 00:41:09,960
You dragons all eat fish, right?

440
00:41:11,520 --> 00:41:13,600
I have a name. Eat and hurry back.

441
00:41:13,680 --> 00:41:16,920
-You won't tell me your name.
-Buxiu.

442
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,480
I'm Twenty-Seven.

443
00:41:21,320 --> 00:41:23,160
Buxiu? Nice name.

444
00:41:23,880 --> 00:41:26,520
Honestly, I kind of envy you dragons.

445
00:41:26,600 --> 00:41:28,080
You're all big and powerful.

446
00:41:28,160 --> 00:41:31,400
When you take human form,
you're quite sturdy.

447
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:34,000
You helped me defeat Sun Liao.

448
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:35,320
I owe you one.

449
00:41:35,400 --> 00:41:36,520
-No need.
-How about this?

450
00:41:36,600 --> 00:41:38,280
I'll grant you three wishes.

451
00:41:39,560 --> 00:41:41,800
No need, don't act on your own.

452
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:48,720
How about this? The first wish
is that I go fishing with you.

453
00:42:09,680 --> 00:42:13,440
Ming Yi, you're finally back.
How did it go?

454
00:42:15,160 --> 00:42:18,120
I found the recipe,
but we can't gather all the herbs.

455
00:42:18,200 --> 00:42:20,400
Tell me what else is still missing.

456
00:42:20,480 --> 00:42:22,800
I'll search the
whole world's heavenly treasures.

457
00:42:22,880 --> 00:42:25,080
As long as I can save you,
I'll do anything.

458
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:32,280
Immortal Situ, I'm very grateful to you.

459
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:35,160
But fate runs its course,
and each has their destiny.

460
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,600
-Don't trouble yourself.
-You know your way back?

461
00:42:39,840 --> 00:42:41,600
Why are you still standing there?
Hurry inside.

462
00:42:41,680 --> 00:42:43,760
I still need to check the Heavenly Grief
in your body.

463
00:42:45,720 --> 00:42:47,360
Honestly,

464
00:42:47,440 --> 00:42:49,840
you never let me have a moment's peace.

465
00:42:55,520 --> 00:42:57,480
-I'm not seeing you off.
-Master She.

466
00:42:57,560 --> 00:43:00,160
Ming Yi refuses to reveal Golden
Millet Dream's recipe to me.

467
00:43:01,560 --> 00:43:04,400
But I really just want to help.

468
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:06,960
Tell me what herbs are needed.

469
00:43:07,040 --> 00:43:08,720
I'll find a way to get them.

470
00:43:12,480 --> 00:43:15,520
Please, Master She. I must save her.

471
00:43:16,840 --> 00:43:19,040
